reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works perfect for travel!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this small power strip for travel as I travel quite a bit and hotels sometimes don't have adequate outlets or don't have them where I need them to be. It is small and compact making it a nice addition to my suitcase setup. I have used each plug on this unit with no issues and nice charge speed for my tech items. The cord is long enough for me and wraps around nicely for easy packing in the included case. Very happy with my purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Only one thing would make it better...
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for traveling and it has been great! The only thing I wish is that the plug fit more snuggly into the groove. The cord stays in place and stays compact, but I just wish it were more flush with the exterior. This is great for hotel rooms where you can never be sure you'll be able to use their chargers. Charges well; packs well. Would recommend.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for travel
reviews.reviewText: This is a great size to toss in my bag and have extra outlets while traveling. Works perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A travel must have!
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this after seeing something similar on TikTok. I was traveling out of state and was tired of packing a ton of charging blocks and hoping I could find enough outlets in my hotel room. This made charging all my devices so easy and keep them together. I loved the built in usb ports as well. This is now a travel must have for me! It also is pretty compact and no bulky in your luggage!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for multiple devices
reviews.reviewText: I purchased for a cruise because often times the ships do not have enough plus for my needs. It worked perfectly, no issues with bringing it into the ship. It allowed my husband and to both plug in and I also charged my watch and iPad. I love that it has the usb port, usb-c for newer devices as well as regular plugs. I loved it so much that I use it at home on my nightstand. The only negative is that at home it will sometimes fall off my nightstand if I pull the cord too much and it would be nice if it had a way or organize or “contain” the cords. Would recommend!
